This is your sign to do it right now •

INGREDIENTS
Ice Bowls
* Two bowls, one smaller than the other
* Sliced citrus fruits
* Fresh mint
Ice Cream in a Bag
* 600ml double cream
* 1 tsp vanilla essence
* 1 tbsp sprinkles
* Half a bag of ice
* 1/2 cup rock ice
Peaches & Cream Lollies
* 2 cans of peaches
* 200ml cream
* Medium ziplock bags
Frozen Banana Ice Cream
* 4 bananas, cut into chunks and frozen
* Plant based milk
Frozen Watermelon Pops
* 1 large watermelon
* Melted chocolate
* Dessicated coconut

node.text:
Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

CREAMY PARMESAN MUSHROOM CHICKEN 
INGREDIENTS
2 tsp oil
4 chicken breasts
salt to taste
pepper to taste
2 tbsp butter
2 cups chopped mushrooms
2 cloves garlic minced
1/2 cup white wine
2 cups heavy cream
1/2 tsp oregano
1 cup grated parmesan
2 cups chopped spinach
Sliced fresh mozzarella

node.text:
We LOVE a samosa here at @twisted but we know that not everyone has the time to create a dough from scratch - so here are 4 fusion twists on the classic, introudcing traditonal - and VERY untraditonal flavours! Give them a go!

INGREDIENTS
Buffalo Chicken 
Butter 65g
Hot water 0.9 cups
Flour 2 cups
Salt, big pinch
Handful of chives, finely chopped
1 chicken breast, shredded
½ cup hot sauce 
½ cup Butter, melted
1 tsp Garlic powder 
Blue cheese ranch, to serve
 
Sausage Marinara 
3 Pork sausages
½ Onion, diced
3 Garlic cloves, minced
1 tbsp tomato paste
400g tinned tomatoes
½ tsp Oregano 
½ tsp sugar
Splash of balsamic vinegar
Salt and pepper to taste
White bread, 8 slices
Pesto, to serve
 
Crunch-wrap 
500g Ground beef 
1 Onion, diced
2 tsp taco seasoning
Diced tomatoes, onion, and coriander 
Sour cream
Queso 
Tortilla chips 
3 tortillas, halved
Chipotle crema, to serve
 
Butter chicken 
3 Chicken thighs, diced
1 tbsp Butter
1 onion, diced
3 Garlic, minced
1 tbsp Ginger paste 
1 tbsp Tomato paste
400g Chopped tomatoes
2 tbsp Honey 
½ cup Single cream
1 tsp Garam masala 
1 tsp turmeric
1 tsp Cumin 
½ tsp Coriander
3 Roti, halved
Green chutney, to serve

#mealideas #dinnerideas #snack #snacks #buffalochicken  #burger #minifood #midnightsnack #samosa  #foodfusion #indianfood

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 slices of white bread
* 	150g butter
* 	2 tbsp parsley, chopped
* 	2 cloves of garlic, chopped
* 	6 slices of mozzarella
* 	30g butter
* 	30g flour
* 	1/2 tbsp mustard 
* 	1/2 tsp smoked paprika
* 	500ml whole milk
* 	200g macaroni, cooked
* 	150g cheddar, grated
* 	100g mozzarella, grated
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 tsp pepper
* 	1 onion, finely chopped

500g beef mince

4 eggs, whisked
2 cups flour
2 cups seasoned breadcrumbs
Oil for frying
#twistedfood #food #yummy #burgerrecipe #dinnerideas #macncheese #nomnom

You asked for more veggie recipes and boy have we DELIVERED - Save our 4 all time best vegetarian recipes! Here are the ingredients - save the post to your food folder!

Crispy Stuffed Mushroom Burgers

INGREDIENTS
8 Portobello mushroom caps

1 cup mozzarella
1/2 parmesan
6 rashers cooked bacon, chopped (optional!)
2 cloves garlic, minced
1/4 cup chopped chives
1/2 tsp pepper
3/4 cup mayonnaise
Egg Wash
Seasoned Flour
Panko breadcrumbs
Frying oil
Burger toppings

GARLIC MOZZARELLA TOMATO SOUP DIPPERS
INGREDIENTS
24 slices soft white bread
24 pieces pizza mozzarella
1/4 cup flour
1/4 cup water
2 cups finely grated parmesan cheese
1 tsp pepper
1 tbsp finely chopped parsley
1 1/2 tsp garlic powder
Tomato sauce
Oil for frying
3 cups mized tomatoes, quartered if large
4 cloves garlic
1 yellow onion, chopped
3 tbsp olive oil
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
1 tsp sugar
8 slices cheddar or mozzarella cheese
1 3/4 cups vegetable stock

Grilled Cheese Tomato Soup Hedgehog Bread
INGREDIENTS
6 plum tomatoes, halved
10 cherry tomatoes
1 beefsteak tomato, quartered
4 cloves garlic
1 yellow onion, chopped
3 tbsp olive oil
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
8 slices cheddar or mozzarella cheese
1 3/4 cups vegetable stock
1 loaf soft French bread loaf
1/4 cup butter, melted
3 crushed garlic cloves
Handful finely chopped parsley

Veggie Big Macs
INGREDIENTS
SERVES 4/ MAKES 4 BURGERS!

For the sauce:

* 	1/2 cup mayonnaise
* 	1/2 tsp sugar
* 	1/2 tsp garlic powder
* 	1/2 tsp onion powder
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
For the bun:
* 	6 pre-sliced burger buns (1 1/2 per person)
* 	8 slices american cheese
* 	lettuce, shredded
* 	chopped white onion

node.text:
If this isn’t my dinner tonight then I don’t want it! 🤤 
Chicken Parm Mac 'n' Cheese!

INGREDIENTS
2 chicken breasts
150g plain flour
1 tsp dried Italian seasoning
2 eggs, whisked

140g panko breadcrumbs 
30g grated parmesan cheese
Oil for shallow frying

30g butter
30g flour
500ml milk
½ tsp mustard powder
¼ tsp paprika
tsp nutmeg
Salt and pepper to taste
400g cooked macaroni
100g grated mozzarella,
100g grated cheddar
50g grated gruyere

250g tomato pasta sauce 
50g grated mozzarella cheese
Fresh basil leaves

node.text:
Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley 

#staplerecipes #mealprep #foodprep #chefmode #winnerwinnerchickendinner #pantryorganization #recipeshare #chickenfordinner #easyrecipes #noleftovers

* 	2 sirloin steaks, sliced as thin as possible
* 	1 cup cream
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 cup beef stock

* 	1 small onion, finely chopped
* 	2 tsp oil
* 	2 tbsp parsley, finely chopped
* 	lots of chips
* 	salt and pepper, to taste
* 	2 tbsp plain flour
* 	3 tbsp butter
* 	1 tbsp black pepper, freshly ground
* 	1 cup parmesan, grated
